{"tid":1890561,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"雜溝？習溝？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-02-21T09:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T09:29:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5052e498a8764761901288b465caa2eecd631ffb","tid":1890561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200220/20865404/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200220%2F20865404%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=74849bcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200220%2F20865404%2F&h=3222b591\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200220/20865404/</a><br />\n<br />\n雜溝？習溝？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200220/large/1582095820_f5a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582095820_f5a6.jpg&h=b536d335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中科院武漢病毒研究所圖片<br />\n<br />\n誰又是專家？所以對那極度邪惡的武漢肺炎病毒疑慮重重，只知案中有案。幸世上有專家、有良心科研人員揭發、有實名舉報、有神秘郵件、有盜竊收買之奇詭紀錄、有一夜之間銷毀全部檔案之異動、有失蹤人口、有護短歪理、有轉移視線&hellip;&hellip;人算不如天算，真相漸漸揭露。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎是什麼危機？只領導人和研發者心中有數，所以瞞報遲報謊報致一發不可收拾。二次世界大戰，侵華關東軍設731部隊，進行人體病毒實驗細菌戰，「黑太陽」並非過去式，若今時今日生化武器研發成功，「紅太陽」兵不血刃，不費槍炮核彈，成本低殺傷力大，滅絕敵勢，稱霸全球。<br />\n<br />\n部份已曝光的參與者實驗者，看來都是平凡恭順老百姓，貌不驚人，想不到心狠手辣只有黨性沒有人性──終於病毒洩漏，害人反害己，整個中國大陸蒙難，無法救治，集體屠殺更顯人命輕賤，百業蕭條，市況亦死寂&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n究竟非自然的人手加工混合作品，有沙士、愛滋、伊波拉病毒、蝙蝠體內不知名病毒外，還有什麼？人們光顧小吃店有所謂兩溝、三溝，魚肉生菜碗仔翅，那駭人瘟疫是三溝、四溝、雜溝──抑或習溝？只有當事人心知肚明了，無辜者死咗都唔知點解。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"9e239dd022eaa80d58429e1d717e4870b06b5311","tid":1890561,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}